The vulkan package does not provide CMake or Visual Studio integration directly.
However, it can still easily be used.

Visual Studio:
    Include $(VULKAN_SDK)/include to your include path.

CMake provides built in support to find Vulkan:

    # https://cmake.org/cmake/help/latest/module/FindVulkan.html
    find_package(Vulkan REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Vulkan::Vulkan)